name: Inaugural to Paris! WestJet Boeing 787-9 Dreamliner Departure from Calgary Airport
description:
Today, May 17th, WestJet celebrated their second inaugural transatlantic flight with their 787 Dreamliner, with the launch of flights from Calgary to Paris!

Here's their third Boeing 787-9 Dreamliner, C-GUDO, operating the very first WestJet flight #10, departing a rainy Calgary for France! ATC is included as always. Hope you enjoy!
